<h1>About Hang Time</h1>
<p>
	Hang Time is a web application for anyone from high school students
	to your every day soccer mom.  It is a resource which enables users to 
	collaborate to plan events based around the availability of all involved
	parties.<br><br>

	Hang Time was launched in April 2017 by Bits-Please, an up-and-coming coding group, who may have started in ashes, but like the phoenix, they will rise.  While still local to Ohio State, they seek to provide everyone with an easy interface for scheduling group events.
	</p>
<br>
