<h3> Hang Time </h3>
<p>
Hang Time is a web application running which runs on ruby on rails, while utilizing various other gems and frameworks.  These include:
</p>
<ul class="list-inline">
<li><strong>Bootstrap: </strong>A free open source collection of HTML, CSS, and Javascript files, which streamline front-end web development and provides an easy way to have consistent styling across your web page.  To learn more about Bootstrap, click this link:<i>
<%= link_to 'Learn more about Bootstrap', 'https://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/' %></i></li>
<li><strong>Devise:</strong> A rails gem built in a MVC (Model View Controller) pattern on top of Warden, designed for providing authentication service to web applications.  It covers functionality from simple sign in and sign out, to encrypting data, to recovering your lost password. With the many functionalities devise offers through modules, you can customize your authentication service specifically to your needs.  To learn more about Devise, click this link:<i>
<%= link_to 'Learn more about Devise', 'https://github.com/plataformatec/devise' %></i>
</li>
<li><strong>jQuery:</strong> 
A simple Javascript library used to simplify event handling, HTML traversing, Ajax functionality, and animations for web pages.  It simplifies the scripting for HTML on the client-side immensely, through one line methods and much less syntax.  To learn more about jQuery, click this link:<i> 
<%= link_to 'Learn more about jQuery', 'https://www.w3schools.com/jquery/' %>
</i></li>
<li><strong>Ruby on Rails: </strong>
As previously mentioned, Hang Time mainly uses Ruby on Rails to power the web-application.<br> To learn more about Ruby on Rails, visit these sites: 
<ul>
<li> <%= link_to 'Ruby on Rails Overview', 'rubyonrails.org' %> </li>
